e defined in Countries Content sheet. </p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n					<h5>Added On</h5>                                        \r\n					<p>User defined field for product add date to the system.</p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n					<h5>Free Shipping</h5>                                        \r\n					<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product is available for free shipping. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ , â€˜Noâ€™.</p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n					<h5>COD Available</h5>                                        \r\n					<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product is available for Cash on Delivery or not. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ , â€˜Noâ€™.</p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n					<h5>Featured</h5>                                        \r\n					<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product as featured or not. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ , â€˜Noâ€™.</p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n					<h5>Approved</h5>                                        \r\n					<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product as Approved or not. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ , â€˜Noâ€™. Default value should be set as â€™Yesâ€™ to display products in the system.</p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n					<h5>Active</h5>                                        \r\n					<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product as active in the system or not. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ , â€˜Noâ€™. Default value should be set as â€™Yesâ€™.</p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n					<h5>Deleted</h5>                                        \r\n					<p>User defined field to mark a particular product as deleted in the system or not. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ , â€˜Noâ€™. Default value should be set as â€™Noâ€™ to display products in the system.</p>                                    </li>                                \r\n			</ul>                            </li>                            \r\n		<li>                                \r\n			<h3>Product Option Content</h3>                            </li>                            \r\n		<li>                                \r\n			<ul>                                    \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n					<h5>Product Identifier</h5>                                        \r\n					<p>User defined unique identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as Product Identifier defined in the Product Catalog Content sheet. </p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n					<h5>Option Identifier</h5>                                        \r\n					<p>User defined unique identifier for the Option. This field needs to be the same as Option Identifier defined in Option Content sheet. </p>                                    </li>                                \r\n			</ul>                            </li>                            \r\n		<li>                                \r\n			<h3>Product Tag Content</h3>                            </li>                            \r\n		<li>                                \r\n			<ul>                                    \r\n				<li>                  